import React from 'react' import "./hero.css" import Title from '../../common/title/Title' import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next' // import BgAnimation from '../components/common/BackgrooundAnimation/BackgroundAnimation'; const Hero = () => { const [t] = useTranslation("global"); return ( <>
<p>{t("hero.p")}</p> <div className='button' id='languageChange'> <button className='primary-btn' > {t("hero.button")} <i className='fa fa-long-arrow-alt-right'></i> </button> </div> </div> {/* <BgAnimation /> */} </div> </section> </> ) } export default Hero
